 +-- OWG -+- Radiation for an Opened WaveGuide
          |
          +-- OWG.FOR      Main program
          +-- OWG_SUBS.FOR Subroutines
          +-- ELEA.FOR     Elements for anisotropic media.
          +-- EHD_SUBS.FOR Subroutines of the Chapter 4 program EHDEV
          |
          +-- OWG -+-    Rectangular Waveguide opened on a pec plane
          |        |
          |        |     ANALYTIC ABC
          |        |
          |        +-- OWG.TXT     Mesh description file
          |        +-- OWG.FEM     The relative mesh
          |        +-- OWG.AUX     The electromagnetic input file
          |        +-- OWG.OUT     The S11 of the various modes
          |        +-- OWG.PLT     S11 of first mode, ready to be plotted
          |        +-- OWG.RAD     Nodal values of the field on the aperture
          |        +-- OWG.DAT     Field values at lowest frequency
          |        +-- OWG.GNU     Relative Fieldmap
          |        | 
          |        |   PMA
          |        |
          |        +-- OWGA.TXT    Mesh description file
          |        +-- OWGA.FEM    The relative mesh
          |        +-- OWGA_##.AUX The electromagnetic input file,
          |        |               With a ## value for the PMA coefficient
          |        +-- OWGA_##.OUT The relative S11 of the various modes
          |        +-- OWGA_##.PLT S11 of first mode, ready to be plotted
          |        +-- OWGA_##.RAD Nodal values of the field on the aperture
          |        +-- OWGA_##.DAT Field values at lowest frequency
          |        +-- OWGA_##.GNU Relative Fieldmap
          |        
          +-- HORN-+-    Rectangular Horn 
                   |
                   |     ANALYTIC ABC
                   |
                   +-- HORN.TXT     Mesh description file
                   +-- HORN.FEM     The relative mesh
                   +-- HORN.AUX     The electromagnetic input file
                   +-- HORN.OUT     The S11 of the various modes
                   +-- HORN.PLT     S11 of first mode, ready to be plotted
                   +-- HORN.RAD     Nodal values of the field on the aperture
                   +-- HORN.DAT     Field values at lowest frequency
                   +-- HORN.GNU     Relative Fieldmap
		   +-- *D.*         Some of the above files are also present
		   |                with a final 'D', these are relative to 
		   |                the same problem but the analisys has been 
		   |                carried out on a Delaunay regularized
		   |                mesh.
                   | 
                   |   PMA
                   |
                   +-- HORNA.TXT    Mesh description file
                   +-- HORNA.FEM    The relative mesh
                   +-- HORNA_##.AUX The electromagnetic input file,
                   |                 With a ## value for the PMA coefficient
                   +-- HORNA_##.OUT The relative S11 of the various modes
                   +-- HORNA_##.PLT S11 of first mode, ready to be plotted
                   +-- HORNA_##.RAD Nodal values of the field on the aperture
	           |                at lowest frequency
                   +-- HORNA_##.DAT Field values at lowest frequency
                   +-- HORNA_##.GNU Relative Fieldmap
                   +-- *D##.*       Here, again, a 'D' in the file name 
				    indicates a regularized mesh.
